# Performance and Load Testing Report

This report summarizes the findings from the load testing and performance audits conducted on the Qollab application (Frontend, Backend, and ML Service) in a local development environment.

## Executive Summary

| Component | Status | Key Finding |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Frontend** | ✅ Excellent | High accessibility scores (91-98%) and clean semantic HTML. |
| **ML Service** | ✅ Optimal | Handled 900 concurrent users with 3ms mean latency. |
| **Backend** | ⚠️ Bottleneck | Login timeouts detected under moderate load due to high bcrypt rounds. |

---

## 1. Frontend Performance (Lighthouse)

Audits were performed on the primary dashboard pages using a Desktop emulation.

| Page | Accessibility | Best Practices | SEO | Observations |
| :--- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :--- |
| **Dashboard** | 91 | 100 | 100 | Clean structure, minimal layout shift. |
| **Inventory** | 98 | 100 | 100 | Excellent table accessibility and ARIA usage. |
